WEBVTT

00:00:50.780 --> 00:00:55.740
=Sugar and Lies=
(A Different Her: The Women's Trilogy)

00:00:56.820 --> 00:00:59.780
=Episode 17=
=You In The Cracks Of Memory=

00:01:15.420 --> 00:01:18.000
♪That song suddenly started playing♪

00:01:18.560 --> 00:01:20.750
♪And I thought of you again♪

00:01:21.550 --> 00:01:26.460
♪Even though I swore to the world
we were done♪

00:01:27.520 --> 00:01:30.080
♪All my friends laughed at me♪

00:01:30.480 --> 00:01:33.260
♪Why can't I just let it go♪

00:01:34.760 --> 00:01:38.780
♪But how could they ever know
how good you were to me♪

00:01:39.170 --> 00:01:42.180
♪I'm falling into
the swamp of your charm♪

00:01:42.430 --> 00:01:45.080
♪It's painful yet feels so right♪

00:01:45.240 --> 00:01:47.810
♪As the endless night unfolds♪

00:01:47.810 --> 00:01:50.540
♪I toss and turn, can't fall asleep♪

00:01:52.270 --> 00:01:55.460
♪You keep running through my mind♪

00:01:55.460 --> 00:01:58.520
♪Nothing matters more than you♪

00:01:58.770 --> 00:01:59.900
♪Why?♪

00:02:00.360 --> 00:02:04.030
♪Did you hear me say please don't go?♪

00:02:17.200 --> 00:02:18.040
Stop wiping.

00:02:20.680 --> 00:02:21.600
Stop wiping.

00:02:37.360 --> 00:02:38.640
Are you disappointed in me?

00:02:45.800 --> 00:02:47.840
I think losing faith in someone

00:02:48.360 --> 00:02:49.300
hurts much more than

00:02:49.300 --> 00:02:50.720
seeing your dreams fall apart.

00:02:52.120 --> 00:02:54.000
I used to be disappointed in myself.

00:02:57.760 --> 00:02:59.080
For years, I shut myself away.

00:02:59.080 --> 00:03:00.760
I wrote code and traded digital coins.

00:03:01.800 --> 00:03:03.000
Made a lot of money back then.

00:03:05.040 --> 00:03:06.440
I felt like the whole world

00:03:06.440 --> 00:03:07.720
was right under my feet.

00:03:12.680 --> 00:03:13.520
Then one day,

00:03:17.240 --> 00:03:19.080
I lost everything overnight.

00:03:21.160 --> 00:03:22.320
When I woke up after that,

00:03:23.200 --> 00:03:24.760
the first thing I did was drinking.

00:03:27.040 --> 00:03:28.520
Because when I was sober,

00:03:29.840 --> 00:03:31.840
even breathing felt unnecessary.

00:03:33.560 --> 00:03:34.400
And later?

00:03:36.640 --> 00:03:37.480
Later I realized,

00:03:37.480 --> 00:03:39.240
I didn't even have the right to give up.

00:03:46.040 --> 00:03:46.880
Thank you.

00:03:51.440 --> 00:03:52.280
Come on, let's go.

00:03:56.360 --> 00:03:58.120
She's so thin,

00:04:00.080 --> 00:04:01.680
wearing a pair of worn-out high heels.

00:04:01.680 --> 00:04:02.560
Yet she carried

00:04:02.560 --> 00:04:04.280
several boxes,
each one wider than she is.

00:04:07.520 --> 00:04:09.320
All that just to earn

00:04:09.320 --> 00:04:10.680
what I used to make in minutes.

00:04:23.440 --> 00:04:24.640
Giving up is easy,

00:04:26.240 --> 00:04:27.440
but staying strong is cool.

00:04:31.640 --> 00:04:33.080
Whether it's for yourself

00:04:36.480 --> 00:04:37.680
or for someone else.

00:05:13.600 --> 00:05:14.800
Take this money.

00:05:15.560 --> 00:05:16.960
It's enough to open a small shop.

00:05:17.720 --> 00:05:19.000
Go live a good life from now on.

00:05:19.480 --> 00:05:20.320
Ding Daang,

00:05:20.960 --> 00:05:22.560
you've had it tough all these years.

00:05:23.360 --> 00:05:24.320
Go home now.

00:05:24.580 --> 00:05:25.880
Your daughter's waiting for you.

00:05:26.920 --> 00:05:27.920
Thanks for helping me.

00:05:29.360 --> 00:05:30.280
From now on,

00:05:30.880 --> 00:05:32.160
if you ever need me again,

00:05:32.160 --> 00:05:33.280
you know where to find me.

00:05:33.700 --> 00:05:34.700
I'll do my best to help.

00:05:48.520 --> 00:05:49.960
Take the cash and get out.

00:05:50.360 --> 00:05:52.200
Don't ever set foot in my house again.

00:05:56.760 --> 00:05:58.200
With this jinx around here,

00:05:58.520 --> 00:06:00.360
even an invitation
wouldn't get me to come.

00:06:16.520 --> 00:06:18.000
Five million for some peace and quiet.

00:06:19.520 --> 00:06:21.160
Mrs. Yu, you're really kind-hearted.

00:06:22.040 --> 00:06:23.700
The Keep Love funds
will arrive next week.

00:06:23.700 --> 00:06:25.890
The lawyer will go over
the contract with you tomorrow.

00:06:41.440 --> 00:06:42.280
Got it.

00:06:42.360 --> 00:06:43.200
Boss.

00:06:52.320 --> 00:06:53.240
Once we wrap up,

00:06:54.200 --> 00:06:55.280
we'll leave Mancheng.

00:06:56.200 --> 00:06:57.040
Boss.

00:06:57.440 --> 00:06:58.680
I need to tell you something.

00:06:58.960 --> 00:06:59.800
Go on.

00:07:01.240 --> 00:07:02.280
I want to stay here.

00:07:05.560 --> 00:07:06.400
Zhou Haoran.

00:07:08.720 --> 00:07:09.800
You're challenging me again.

00:07:10.560 --> 00:07:11.920
And you didn't stick to the plan.

00:07:12.320 --> 00:07:13.160
Maybe this is fate.

00:07:13.160 --> 00:07:14.010
Fate, oh, fate!

00:07:14.010 --> 00:07:15.480
Tell me, what exactly is fate?

00:07:20.960 --> 00:07:22.200
Then let me tell you.

00:07:25.080 --> 00:07:26.000
Keep Love.

00:07:26.680 --> 00:07:27.920
That's fate.

00:07:36.400 --> 00:07:37.240
Don't cross the line.

00:07:56.000 --> 00:07:56.840
Sorry.

00:08:02.160 --> 00:08:03.800
It'll be over soon.

00:08:03.800 --> 00:08:04.640
You have my word.

00:08:22.000 --> 00:08:23.080
Did he apologize?

00:08:23.320 --> 00:08:24.440
Did I hear that right?

00:08:27.000 --> 00:08:28.440
His data value dropped.

00:08:28.440 --> 00:08:30.160
It's back to 32%.

00:08:30.480 --> 00:08:32.840
He must've had doubts,

00:08:32.840 --> 00:08:34.560
trying to find a way to fight back.

00:08:35.720 --> 00:08:36.920
Stay steady, no matter what.

00:09:06.160 --> 00:09:07.000
Brother.

00:09:07.080 --> 00:09:07.920
What brings you here?

00:09:10.000 --> 00:09:11.000
Hu Yitong came by.

00:09:11.920 --> 00:09:12.860
How could that happen?

00:09:19.680 --> 00:09:21.000
Don't hide anything from me.

00:09:22.000 --> 00:09:24.080
Otherwise, I won't help you
with anything.

00:09:25.760 --> 00:09:26.600
Brother.

00:09:26.800 --> 00:09:27.880
If we go through with this,

00:09:27.880 --> 00:09:29.760
can we really win Hu Yitong's heart back?

00:09:36.200 --> 00:09:37.040
Remember,

00:09:37.880 --> 00:09:40.200
doing as you're told
is your only option.

00:09:42.040 --> 00:09:42.880
Otherwise,

00:09:45.640 --> 00:09:47.320
I've got plenty of ways to deal with you.

00:09:54.680 --> 00:09:55.760
Why didn't anyone tell me

00:09:55.760 --> 00:09:57.240
Hu Yitong and Miaomiao met?

00:09:59.640 --> 00:10:01.640
The system... got disrupted.

00:10:01.640 --> 00:10:03.440
Someone blocked their location.

00:10:03.440 --> 00:10:04.320
Lin Xibei!

00:10:06.560 --> 00:10:07.920
How could you miss

00:10:07.920 --> 00:10:08.760
such an obvious flaw?

00:10:09.520 --> 00:10:10.360
Boss,

00:10:10.720 --> 00:10:12.680
maybe Miaomiao's got her own plan.

00:10:15.720 --> 00:10:16.920
Her own plan?

00:10:17.760 --> 00:10:19.080
So you did it on purpose.

00:10:26.020 --> 00:10:28.380
(Warning: Ding Daang's car accident)

00:10:30.360 --> 00:10:31.240
It's Ding Daang.

00:10:45.840 --> 00:10:47.080
- What happened?
- Ding Daang!

00:10:47.560 --> 00:10:48.400
Ding Daang!

00:10:54.160 --> 00:10:55.080
Stay back.

00:10:55.600 --> 00:10:56.440
Go away.

00:10:56.840 --> 00:10:57.720
Get out.

00:11:19.520 --> 00:11:21.040
Don't look at me like that.

00:11:21.760 --> 00:11:22.920
She's hurt.

00:11:28.080 --> 00:11:29.240
Don't you feel anything?

00:11:30.480 --> 00:11:31.480
Shut up.

00:11:33.800 --> 00:11:35.040
It's you.

00:11:36.720 --> 00:11:37.640
Chen Aming.

00:11:39.480 --> 00:11:41.320
This is all your fault.

00:11:43.320 --> 00:11:44.280
You're scared now.

00:11:45.680 --> 00:11:46.520
Scared?

00:11:50.880 --> 00:11:51.920
What would I be scared of?

00:11:53.800 --> 00:11:54.720
What's there

00:11:56.040 --> 00:11:57.120
to be afraid of?

00:11:58.720 --> 00:12:00.080
Then why are you crying?

00:12:04.640 --> 00:12:05.520
Just admit it.

00:12:08.480 --> 00:12:09.680
You're in love with her.

00:12:11.440 --> 00:12:12.280
You

00:12:13.920 --> 00:12:14.760
love her.

00:12:15.400 --> 00:12:16.280
Don't get mad.

00:12:16.800 --> 00:12:18.880
I don't care about your messed-up plans.

00:12:19.520 --> 00:12:21.480
I just want Ding Daang to be safe.

00:12:22.160 --> 00:12:25.080
Chen Aming.

00:12:30.880 --> 00:12:31.840
Chen Miaomiao.

00:12:32.520 --> 00:12:33.360
I'm warning you.

00:12:33.880 --> 00:12:35.040
This is the last time.

00:12:35.880 --> 00:12:37.080
The wounds on Ding Daang.

00:12:38.240 --> 00:12:39.720
Do you really think I don't know?

00:12:40.200 --> 00:12:41.400
You're the one who pushed her.

00:12:41.880 --> 00:12:42.960
She took Hu Yitong away.

00:12:42.960 --> 00:12:44.520
Now she's trying to take you too.

00:12:45.280 --> 00:12:46.160
I hate her.

00:13:12.480 --> 00:13:19.480
♪I forgot this is a movie meant for one♪

00:13:23.880 --> 00:13:31.240
♪Somehow you're still here,
crying with me♪

00:13:35.690 --> 00:13:37.630
♪They say♪

00:13:38.040 --> 00:13:46.420
♪Lovers should never hold hands
while watching a sad movie♪

00:13:46.940 --> 00:13:49.920
♪Some endings cannot be changed♪

00:13:50.140 --> 00:13:56.090
♪They don't belong in sweet memories♪

00:13:57.470 --> 00:14:03.230
♪I've already lost you♪

00:14:03.230 --> 00:14:08.710
♪Thinking of it takes my breath away♪

00:14:09.010 --> 00:14:14.960
♪The movie ends, so many couples around♪

00:14:14.960 --> 00:14:19.740
♪Yet none were ever like us♪

00:14:20.850 --> 00:14:24.880
♪The past will always pass♪

00:14:25.210 --> 00:14:32.790
♪If you could still hold me tight
in your arms♪

00:14:33.260 --> 00:14:36.510
♪I'd believe
that there are miracles in love♪

00:14:37.070 --> 00:14:42.720
♪I'd prove
that I'm still in love with you♪

00:14:45.180 --> 00:14:48.710
♪I've learned how to cherish
what we had♪

00:14:48.710 --> 00:14:54.970
♪But sadly, it's not you♪